        >
          <img
            src="/images/catalog/photo-tapis-clean.webp"
            alt="Residential carpet cleaning"
            class="card-img"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="card-icon icon-blue">🏠</div>
            <h3>Residential Carpet</h3>
            <p>
              Restore color and hygiene to your wool, synthetic, or oriental
