            </p>
            <span class="link-text">See details &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- 4. Tapis Synthétique -->
        <a
          href="/services/tapis-synthetique"
          class="service-card-modern fade-in-section delay-100"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/catalog/photo-47.webp"
            alt="Synthetic carpet cleaning"
            class="card-img"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="card-icon icon-blue">🧹</div>
            <h3>Synthetic Carpet Cleaning at Home</h3>
            <p>Technique adapted to modern and resistant fibers.</p>
            <span class="link-text">See details &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- 5. Tapis en Laine -->
        <a
          href="/services/tapis-laine"
          class="service-card-modern fade-in-section delay-200"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/catalog/photo-22.webp"
            alt="Wool carpet cleaning"
            class="card-img"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="card-icon icon-blue">🧶</div>
            <h3>Wool Carpets</h3>
            <p>
              Delicate and specialized treatment for your wool and natural fiber
              carpets.
            </p>
            <span class="link-text">See details &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- 6. Tapis Orientaux -->
        <a
          href="/services/tapis-orientaux"
          class="service-card-modern fade-in-section delay-300"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/catalog/photo-oriental-custom.webp"
            alt="Oriental carpet cleaning"
            class="card-img"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="card-icon icon-blue">🏺</div>
            <h3>Oriental Carpet Cleaning at Home</h3>
            <p>Expert restoration for Persian and Oriental rugs.</p>
            <span class="link-text">See details &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- 7. Tapis Commercial -->
        <a
          href="/services/nettoyage-tapis-commercial"
          class="service-card-modern fade-in-section delay-100"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/catalog/tapis-commercial-combo.webp"
            alt="Commercial carpet cleaning"
            class="card-img"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="card-icon icon-blue">🏢</div>
            <h3>Commercial Carpet Cleaning</h3>
            <p>Solutions for offices and large spaces.</p>
            <span class="link-text">See details &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- 8. Matelas -->
        <a
          href="/services/nettoyage-desinfection-matelas"
          class="service-card-modern fade-in-section delay-200"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/catalog/photo-matelas-custom.webp"
            alt="Mattress cleaning"
            class="card-img"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="card-icon icon-red">🛏️</div>
            <h3>Mattress Cleaning & Disinfection</h3>
            <p>
              Certified elimination of dust mites and bacteria for healthy
              sleep.
            </p>
            <span class="link-text">See details &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- 9. Céramique -->
        <a
          href="/services/nettoyage-tuiles-ceramique"
          class="service-card-modern fade-in-section delay-300"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/catalog/photo-78.webp"
            alt="Tile and grout cleaning"
            class="card-img"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="card-icon icon-blue">✨</div>
            <h3>Tiles & Grout</h3>
            <p>
              Restore the shine of your floors and joints with our high-pressure
              cleaning.
            </p>
            <span class="link-text">See details &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- 10. Protecteur -->
        <a
          href="/services/protecteur"
          class="service-card-modern fade-in-section delay-100"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/catalog/photo-20.webp"
            alt="Stain protector"
            class="card-img"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="card-icon icon-blue">☔</div>
            <h3>Stain Protector Application</h3>
            <p>
              Teflon/Scotchgard protection for fabrics, leather, and carpets.
            </p>
            <span class="link-text">See details &rarr;</span>
          </div>
