            >biodegradable and non-toxic products</strong
          >.
        </p>

        <ul class="eco-list">
          <li>
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-8.webp"
              alt="Certification"
              class="icon-cert"
              style="width: 50px; height: auto;"
            />
            <div>
              <strong>Certified Ecological</strong><br />Approved and safe
              products.
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="check-green">👶</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Hypoallergenic</strong><br />Ideal for asthmatics.
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="check-green">🐾</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Pet Friendly</strong><br />Your pets can roam freely.
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="eco-image-wrapper fade-in-section delay-100">
        <div class="eco-circle-bg"></div>
        <img
          src="/images/catalog/photo-76.webp"
          alt="Produits écologiques nettoyage"
          class="eco-img floating"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 5. LA PUISSANCE (Fond Bleu Foncé - Tech - Sérieux) -->
