          <div class="tech-gallery">
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-10.webp"
              alt="Truck Mount Technology"
              class="tech-img"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-5.webp"
              alt="Specialized Equipment"
              class="tech-img"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-56-rotated.webp"
              alt="Professional Intervention"
              class="tech-img"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>

          <p class="description-text">
            Our results are superior because we make no compromises on
