          </p>

          <ul class="power-list">
            <li>
              <span class="check-icon">✓</span>
              <strong>20x more powerful</strong> than standard equipment
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="check-icon">✓</span>
              <strong>98% moisture extraction</strong> for fast drying
            </li>
          </ul>

          <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
            <p class="video-cta-text">Discover our expertise in action:</p>
            <div class="social-links">
              <a
                href="https://www.facebook.com/NettoyageEmpire"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener"
                aria-label="Facebook"
                class="social-btn fb"
              >
                <svg
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
